{"type":"text","timestamp":1775879614181,"sessionID":"ses_2855489bfffepMF5gVOLHbLILq","part":{"id":"prt_d7aac3f61001CFKdpQmk4E8UVE","messageID":"msg_d7aac2d7d001j2suRZE9UJlzBB","sessionID":"ses_2855489bfffepMF5gVOLHbLILq","type":"text","text":"Based on my verification against the spec AR-036, here are the findings:\n\n## Verification Results\n\n### ✅ Files Present (Complete)\nAll required files per spec are present:\n- `main.py`, `manifest.yaml`, `provider/agentcube.yaml`, `provider/agentcube.py`\n- `tools/agentcube-code-interpreter.yaml`, `tools/agentcube-code-interpreter.py`\n- `requirements.txt`, `GUIDE.md`, `README.md`, `PRIVACY.md`, `.difyignore`\n\n### ✅ manifest.yaml - Matches Spec\n- `version`: 0.0.2 ✓\n- `type`: plugin ✓\n- `author`: volcano-sh ✓\n- `name`: agentcube ✓\n- `label`: multilingual (en_US, ja_JP, zh_Hans, pt_BR) ✓\n- `description`: multilingual strings ✓\n- `icon`: icon.png ✓\n- `icon_dark`: icon-dark.png ✓\n- `resource`: memory + permission subtree ✓\n- `plugins.tools`: [provider/agentcube.yaml] ✓\n- `meta`: version, arch (amd64, arm64), runner (python 3.12), entrypoint ✓\n\n### ✅ provider/agentcube.yaml - Matches Spec\n- `identity`: author, name, label, description, icon ✓\n- Commented `oauth_schema` block (not active) ✓\n- `tools`: [tools/agentcube-code-interpreter.yaml] ✓\n- `extra.python.source`: provider/agentcube.py ✓\n\n### ✅ tools/agentcube-code-interpreter.yaml - Matches Spec\nAll 8 parameters with correct types, required flags, and form types:\n- `router_url` (string, required, form) ✓\n- `workload_manager_url` (string, required, form) ✓\n- `language` (select, false, llm, options: python/javascript/typescript) ✓\n- `code` (string, false, llm) ✓\n- `command` (string, false, llm) ✓\n- `session_id` (string, false, llm) ✓\n- `session_reuse` (boolean, false, llm) ✓\n- `code_interpreter_id` (string, false, llm) ✓\n\n### ✅ provider/agentcube.py - Matches Spec\n- Class `AgentcubeCodeInterpreterProvider(ToolProvider)` ✓\n- `_validate_credentials` method implemented with credential validation ✓\n- Uses `ToolProviderCredentialValidationError` ✓\n\n### ✅ main.py - Matches Spec\n- `Plugin(DifyPluginEnv(MAX_REQUEST_TIMEOUT=120)).run()` ✓\n\n### ❌ Lint Issues Found\n7 ruff errors (deprecation warnings for typing module):\n- Using `Dict` instead of `dict` (UP035/UP006)\n- Using `Generator` from typing instead of collections.abc\n- Unused `Optional` import\n\n**Recommendation**: Fix lint errors for better code quality.\n\n### Tests\nNo tests found in the codebase. Consider adding tests for the provider and tool classes.","time":{"start":1775879614178,"end":1775879614178}}}
